description:
Raymundo and Lunchbox are mad that Hillary got a pair of 'Luke Combs Crocs' sent to her by the record label, but they didn't. Bobby is struggling with something for his wedding that's rather customary for most people. Plus, we reveal the embarrassing beauty secrets we do to keep ourselves looking good!
